Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uBrigadier Jay Naicker, uthe abasebenzi bendawo eyibhizinisi esemgwaqweni uMoses Mabhida, eMgungundlovu, bebevula ekuseni ngesikhathi kuthushuka amadoda amabili. Kuthiwa abakhombe “ngesibhamu” afuna izikhiye zokuvula isitolo abe esevalela abasebenzi ngaphakathi ebafuna imali ngodli. Ababone lokhu kwenzeka babikele amaphoyisa abeseduze enomkhankaso wesikhathi samaholidi. Amaphoyisa avule ngenkani umnyango wesitolo angena ngaphakathi. Kuboshwe amadoda amabili aneminyaka ewu-27 no-38 atholwe esecashe ophahleni lwesitolo. Batholwe nesibhamu sethoyizi nemali ebeyebiwe ngesikhathi bebamba inkunzi. Kuvulwe icala lokubamba inkunzi ibhizinisi.